claim.claim-text:
5. A liquid dispensing hairbrush device comprising:
a body comprised of a cap, an interior container and a bottom surface having an opening;
a brush head comprised of a top surface having an opening;
a nub having an opening and positioned on the top surface; and
a fastener positioned on each of the top and bottom surfaces.

17. A method of using a liquid dispensing hairbrush device to apply a liquid to a user's hair, the method comprising:
opening a cap of a body of the liquid dispensing hairbrush device to access an interior container;
filling the interior container with the liquid;
closing the cap; and
applying the liquid dispensing hairbrush device to the user's hair to allow the liquid to flow through an opening in a nub of the liquid dispensing hairbrush device and onto the user's hair.
